OL,3,CFormer boxer pleads guilty to
OL,4,C'violently' murdering 'gentle soul'
OL,6,FA former boxer has admitted
OL,7,F"violently" murdering a 46-year-old
OL,8,Fman described by his family as a
OL,9,F"gentle soul".
OL,11,FAdam Bowers pleaded guilty on Friday
OL,12,Fat Bristol Crown Court to murdering
OL,13,FNick Bryan at a property in Rydal
OL,14,FRoad, , in November 2021.
OL,16,FHe launched a violent and sustained
OL,17,Fattack on Mr Bryan by punching and
OL,18,Fkicking him, after several people had
OL,19,Fbeen drinking at the address on the
OL,20,Fevening of 15 November. He then fled
OL,21,Fthe scene.
