OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fproperty in the early hours of the
OL,8,Ffollowing morning, where Mr Bryan was
OL,9,Ffound unconscious.
OL,11,FHe was taken to hospital, where he
OL,12,Fsadly died on 17 November.
OL,14,FA post-mortem examination revealed Mr
OL,15,FBryan had died after sustaining
OL,16,Fsignificant head injuries.
OL,18,FPolice said the pathologist was unable
OL,19,Fto rule out whether Bowers had also
OL,20,Fused a blunt weapon to inflict the
OL,21,Ffatal injuries.
