OL,6,FMr Bryan, who used to live in , was
OL,7,Fdescribed as a "bright, beautiful,
OL,8,Fgentle soul", by his family.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Roger
OL,11,FDoxsey, from Avon and Somerset Police,
OL,12,Fsaid: "Adam Bowers subjected Nick
OL,13,FBryan to a violent attack before
OL,14,Ffleeing the scene without any attempt
OL,15,Fto get medical attention to help the
OL,16,Fman he had critically injured.
