OL,6,F"The Major Crime Investigation Team
OL,7,Fhas conducted a thorough inquiry into
OL,8,Fwhat happened that night and that hard
OL,9,Fwork saw sufficient evidence be
OL,10,Fgathered to ensure Bowers has pleaded
OL,11,Fguilty to murder.
OL,13,F"A family liaison officer continues to
OL,14,Foffer support to Mr Bryan's family and
OL,15,Four thoughts remain with them. We hope
OL,16,Ftoday's plea provides them with some
OL,17,Fcomfort and answers around what
OL,18,Fhappened on that fateful night, which
OL,19,Fthey deserve to know.
